## DAX CODE

```DAX
MEASURE 'Measures Table'[ColorTransparent] = "#FFFFFF00"
MEASURE 'Measures Table'[ColorNegativos] = "#a81917"
MEASURE 'Measures Table'[ColorPositivos] = "#3c8a37"
MEASURE 'Measures Table'[ColorNeutros] = "#fbfbfb"
MEASURE 'Measures Table'[ColorNeutrosMorado] = "#7c7dff"
MEASURE 'Measures Table'[ColorNeutrosAzul] = "#0078d4"
MEASURE 'Measures Table'[ColorGris1] = "#d3d3d3"
MEASURE 'Measures Table'[ColorGris2] = "#bfbfbf"
MEASURE 'Measures Table'[ColorGris3] = "#e5e5e5"
